{
  "stem": "1479.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When-- in '38 when the Germans occupied Czechoslovakia, he joined the Nazi party, no question about it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He became very active in the-- in the party.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when Germany occupied Poland, he certainly came to Poland with one purpose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was an opportunist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He came to Poland to make a fortune.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oskar Schindler was a man who loved money, who loved women, who loved to drink, who loved to smoke.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He always cared to be the center of attraction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "His charm-- with his charm-- and to top everything off, he was a master in bribery.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And with his charm and knowing how to bribe, he achieved the impossible, the unbelievable thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Number two, very few people know about it, how he grew up, where he grew up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I will tell you later on, a neighbor of my sister in Israel heard from this neighbor the details because this gentleman grew up with Schindler in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Oskar Schindler and his sister Adeline, they grew up in a neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They played.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They went to school with two other little boys their age.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the father of the two boys was a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Schindler was always a restless boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When he was in trouble with his father, he would run to the rabbi for help.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he actually grew up knowing that Jews have no horns, that Jews are human beings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this, I believe, did reflect-- in spite that he came to make money, in spite-- because using people for forced labor, it had a purpose.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "By doing this, he was saving our lives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was-- as I say, he loved to be the center of attraction.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We must remember and never forget.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
